  "description": [
    "Page 4 YOUNG NISEI VETS FLAY BILBO AND RANKIN AT TESTIMONIAL DINNER CHICAGO June 8 ANP Rankin and Bilbo known as Ameri cas leading race baiters were flayed here by young Japanese American war veterans during a testimonial dinner in honor of their war dead at the Stevens hotel Fighting racism as he had fought fascism militant young Ben Ku roki a former tail gunner on Americas bombers during the war denounced racial bigotry and with it denounced Bilbo and Rankin He bitterly criticized this nations over all jim crow pattern against minority groups and declared that Japanese Americans are the worst persecuted minority in this coun try Kuroki known as the Boy from Nebraska made 58 missions dur ing the war as his contribution to the preservation of the American way of life I have heard people say that the boys did not know what they were fighting for he told his 1000 listeners I know what I was fight THE STAR SAY MARKET REPORT Saturday June 8 1946 STOCK BOND 96i 458 VKAVIM FORTIFIED Vitamins ABCDG in cluding the entire B Complex in full dosage for year round health 30 and 60day treatment 195345 Stops pain at once"
  ],
